Class ModifyContractTransactionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.TransactionBuilder<ModifyContractTransactionBuilder,​ModifyContractTransaction>
      • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.ModifyContractTransactionBuilder
  • public class ModifyContractTransactionBuilder
extends TransactionBuilder<ModifyContractTransactionBuilder,​ModifyContractTransaction>

    builder for ModifyContractTransaction

    Standard use: contract needs to be identified by the contentHash. To create contract call init(String, BigInteger) followed by definition of customers, executors and verifiers
